Ability

AbilityScriptObject
  -Framework of an ability
  -Uses building blocks for exampel, the abilitys effects, filter, and how it find targets
  
AfflictionAbility
  -Framework of an affliction (Buff/Debuff)
  -Uses building blocks for exampel, modify stats, deal damage, and gain health
  -Affliction can call building blocks in different events such as, there is a duplicate affliction, affliction ends.

AfflictionHandler
  -Handles AfflictionAbilitys such as when adding, removing, updating affliction.
  -Contain the Open Legend action to resist afflictions.
